data.description: Secure a lower-than-market interest rate.  The existing property taxes do not include any exemptions or deductions. The seller is willing to implement a 2/1 interest rate buydown, resulting in reduced payments for the first and second years.  This delightful three-bedroom, two-bathroom home nestled in Franklin Township offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and convenience. The open-concept living area creates a welcoming space for everyday living and entertaining, flooded with natural light. The generously-sized master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom, ensuring a private and luxurious retreat. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family members, guests, or a home office.  Current property taxes have NO exemptions.    Outside, the fenced backyard provides a secure and private area for outdoor activities, with the added serenity of a pond view. Just a block away, you'll find a community pool and playground for recreational enjoyment. This home is also within the Franklin Township school district, offering a top-notch education for your family. With easy access to the interstate and downtown Indianapolis, three city parks nearby, and the Greenwood Park Mall only 5 miles away, this property offers a well-rounded and convenient lifestyle. Additionally, the large 2.5-car garage provides ample storage space for your vehicles and hobbies. A perfect place for a home, combining modern living with a tranquil setting.
